        <updateDate>2007-10-05T17:46:53Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Property Tax Relief Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow state and local real property taxes paid on a principal residence as a deduction from gross income (thus allowing taxpayers who do not itemize their tax deductions to claim such deduction).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
